TicTacToe Psuedocode

  Declare Variables

    Make a Table System for the board
      Array
      Parts of Array

  Integrate Turn System

      turn variable

  Determine Whether Turn is even or odd for X/0

  Loop

    Input User Decision X/0 on the board

          if turn is even print 0's

          if turn is odd print out X's

    Print out decision and past decisions

        print array

    Test to see if anyone won

      if anyone won break out of loop

    increment turn

  end of loop

    if tie
      print out tie and board again

    if win
      print out winner and board again
